\f1\b\fs48 \cf0 Dire\'e7\'e3o est\'e9tica principal\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 A HUD deve parecer uma combina\'e7\'e3o de:\

\f1\b di\'e1rio de pesquisa + ficha de observa\'e7\'e3o + caderno de campo + adesivos/etiquetas marinhas.
\f0\b0 \
Refer\'eancias mentais:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
caderno de bi\'f3logo com anota\'e7\'f5es;\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
etiquetas de esp\'e9cimes;\
\ls1\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
